hopefully from Egypt;

00:13:31.080 --> 00:13:35.130 align:middle line:84%
that's a whole other story--
the torsion phenomenon that we

00:13:35.130 --> 00:13:40.240 align:middle line:84%
see with Venus crossing the
sun that we were actually

00:13:40.240 --> 00:13:45.930 align:middle line:84%
able to measure during the
2003 transit eight years ago.

00:13:45.930 --> 00:13:46.790 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: Hm.

