is, the interaction

00:36:02.370 --> 00:36:05.100 align:middle line:84%
between those massive
spinning generators,

00:36:05.100 --> 00:36:08.530 align:middle line:84%
which are feeding current
at 60 cycles per second

00:36:08.530 --> 00:36:11.490 align:middle line:84%
into the grid from
southern Nevada

00:36:11.490 --> 00:36:13.600 align:middle line:84%
to the entire
American Southwest,

00:36:13.600 --> 00:36:17.870 align:middle line:84%
should show up as ripples
in your house current, which

00:36:17.870 --> 00:36:20.240 align:middle line:84%
means that, potentially,
millions of people

00:36:20.240 --> 00:36:23.400 align:middle line:84%
