we will no longer

00:47:07.760 --> 00:47:11.250 align:middle line:84%
have young Americans
dying in resource wars

00:47:11.250 --> 00:47:13.469 align:middle line:84%
like Iraq, which
was fought for oil.

00:47:13.469 --> 00:47:14.260 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: That's good.

00:47:14.260 --> 00:47:15.410 align:middle line:84%
>>HOAGLAND: We can
bring them home.

00:47:15.410 --> 00:47:17.630 align:middle line:84%
We don't have to have
them all over the world,

00:47:17.630 --> 00:47:21.560 align:middle line:84%
defending an empire that is
based on a false premise.

00:47:21.560 --> 00:47:24.130 align:middle line:84%
This physics will allow,
when it matriculates

00:47:24.130 --> 00:47:28.600 align:middle line:84%
in the public arena into
an appropriate technology,

00:47:28.600 --> 00:47:31.670 align:middle line:84%
an ability to create
electricity out of the ether,

00:47:31.670 --> 00:47:33.150 align:middle line:90%
out of the vacuum.

00:47:33.150 --> 00:47:36.870 align:middle line:84%
And ether energy,
ether electricity

00:47:36.870 --> 00:47:39.330 align:middle line:90%
is inherently non-pollutionous.

00:47:39.330 --> 00:47:41.820 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't turn into waste heat.

00:47:41.820 --> 00:47:43.650 align:middle line:84%
That's another key
aspect of this,

00:47:43.650 --> 00:47:46.810 align:middle line:84%
because, if you really open the
gates to a higher dimension,

00:47:46.810 --> 00:47:48.630 align:middle line:90%
you wind up killing entropy.

00:47:48.630 --> 00:47:50.920 align:middle line:84%
That's why, for instance--
I'm going to widely diverge

00:47:50.920 --> 00:47:54.010 align:middle line:84%
here-- the reports of
ghostly phenomenon--

00:47:54.010 --> 00:47:56.510 align:middle line:84%
which, again, is part
of the torsion field--

00:47:56.510 --> 00:47:58.852 align:middle line:84%
they have a lowered
lower temperature.

00:47:58.852 --> 00:48:00.560 align:middle line:84%
You'll talk about,
oh, there was a chill.

00:48:00.560 --> 00:48:00.990 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: Oh, right.

00:48:00.990 --> 00:48:02.365 align:middle line:84%
>>HOAGLAND: Why
is there a chill?

00:48:02.365 --> 00:48:04.630 align:middle line:84%
It's because entropy
goes out the window.

00:48:04.630 --> 00:48:06.470 align:middle line:84%
When you get more
ordered, you get

00:48:06.470 --> 00:48:08.740 align:middle line:90%
random thermal motion ceases.

00:48:08.740 --> 00:48:10.680 align:middle line:84%
Therefore, the
temperature goes down.

00:48:10.680 --> 00:48:14.710 align:middle line:84%
Therefore, it's a measure of
the coherence between a higher

00:48:14.710 --> 00:48:17.270 align:middle line:84%
dimension and an
unlimited source of energy

00:48:17.270 --> 00:48:19.240 align:middle line:90%
and our limited 3D reality.

00:48:19.240 --> 00:48:21.350 align:middle line:84%
There's no limit
to the implications

00:48:21.350 --> 00:48:23.195 align:middle line:84%
of measuring and
proving this physics.

00:48:23.195 --> 00:48:24.570 align:middle line:84%
And that's what
we're going to be

00:48:24.570 --> 00:48:26.989 align:middle line:90%
doing very publicly this Sunday.

00:48:26.989 --> 00:48:28.280 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: Well, good luck on that.

