I hope you succeed
in what you find.

00:48:30.072 --> 00:48:32.530 align:middle line:84%
>>HOAGLAND: Well, I bet you're
going to ask me to come back

00:48:32.530 --> 00:48:33.075 align:middle line:90%
and show you--

00:48:33.075 --> 00:48:34.283 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: Oh, I am going to ask.

