What's your expectations for it?

00:48:41.432 --> 00:48:42.390 align:middle line:90%
What's going to happen?

00:48:42.390 --> 00:48:44.280 align:middle line:84%
>>HOAGLAND: Exactly the
opposite of all the doomsayers.

00:48:44.280 --> 00:48:44.780 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: Good.

00:48:44.780 --> 00:48:45.340 align:middle line:90%
I like that.

00:48:45.340 --> 00:48:47.040 align:middle line:84%
>>HOAGLAND: I think that
the Mayans were trying

00:48:47.040 --> 00:48:48.470 align:middle line:84%
to tell us--
remember, "apocalypse"

00:48:48.470 --> 00:48:49.595 align:middle line:90%
doesn't mean "catastrophe."

00:48:49.595 --> 00:48:51.810 align:middle line:90%
It means "enlightenment."

00:48:51.810 --> 00:48:54.080 align:middle line:90%
It means "the veil lifting."

00:48:54.080 --> 00:48:56.860 align:middle line:84%
We are in a race between
the physics of reality--

00:48:56.860 --> 00:49:00.900 align:middle line:84%
meaning entropy, 3D
geology, meteorology stuff--

00:49:00.900 --> 00:49:03.190 align:middle line:84%
and the physics of the
torsion field interaction

00:49:03.190 --> 00:49:05.170 align:middle line:90%
with consciousness.

00:49:05.170 --> 00:49:07.290 align:middle line:84%
And the consciousness
is going to win,

00:49:07.290 --> 00:49:11.050 align:middle line:84%
because we respond the quickest
of all these physical systems.

00:49:11.050 --> 00:49:14.680 align:middle line:84%
That's why you're watching
things like the Flynn effect

00:49:14.680 --> 00:49:16.900 align:middle line:84%
and like politicians,
who, somehow, even

00:49:16.900 --> 00:49:18.800 align:middle line:84%
against their
better judgment, are

00:49:18.800 --> 00:49:21.149 align:middle line:84%
forced to tell the-- remember,
a gaffe in Washington

00:49:21.149 --> 00:49:22.690 align:middle line:84%
is when a politician
tells the truth.

00:49:22.690 --> 00:49:22.960 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: Yeah.

00:49:22.960 --> 00:49:25.372 align:middle line:84%
>>HOAGLAND: Well, you notice
it happening more and more.

00:49:25.372 --> 00:49:26.330 align:middle line:90%
That's not an accident.

00:49:26.330 --> 00:49:29.310 align:middle line:84%
That's part of this
changing physics

00:49:29.310 --> 00:49:31.310 align:middle line:90%
that we're all caught up in.

00:49:31.310 --> 00:49:33.700 align:middle line:84%
The bright ones, the sharp
ones, the smart ones,

00:49:33.700 --> 00:49:36.090 align:middle line:84%
the conscious ones
will reach out now

00:49:36.090 --> 00:49:38.360 align:middle line:84%
for explanations as to
why this is occurring

00:49:38.360 --> 00:49:41.120 align:middle line:84%
and how they can make it occur
more often in their own lives.

00:49:41.120 --> 00:49:43.400 align:middle line:84%
>>JAY: Well, lying is an
unnatural thing anyway.

00:49:43.400 --> 00:49:43.960 align:middle line:90%
So--

00:49:43.960 --> 00:49:45.240 align:middle line:84%
>>HOAGLAND: We have to
keep remembering the lie.

00:49:45.240 --> 00:49:45.530 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: Yeah.

00:49:45.530 --> 00:49:47.080 align:middle line:84%
You've got to keep
remembering all your lies.

00:49:47.080 --> 00:49:48.370 align:middle line:90%
And then it gets impossible.

00:49:48.370 --> 00:49:51.137 align:middle line:84%
So I think it's a
big relief, probably,

00:49:51.137 --> 00:49:52.970 align:middle line:84%
to be able to tell the
truth for these guys.

00:49:52.970 --> 00:49:54.044 align:middle line:90%
Don't you think?

00:49:54.044 --> 00:49:55.960 align:middle line:84%
>>HOAGLAND: I don't think
it's that conscious.

00:49:55.960 --> 00:49:56.240 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: Yeah, I don't, either.

00:49:56.240 --> 00:49:58.320 align:middle line:84%
>>HOAGLAND: I think it's
just like "Liar Liar."

00:49:58.320 --> 00:49:59.340 align:middle line:90%
Remember Jim Carrey?

00:49:59.340 --> 00:50:00.390 align:middle line:90%
Phenomenal movie.

00:50:00.390 --> 00:50:00.910 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: Yeah.

00:50:00.910 --> 00:50:02.701 align:middle line:84%
>>HOAGLAND: That's what
I think's going on.

00:50:02.701 --> 00:50:05.552 align:middle line:84%
In fact, if I was slightly
conspiratorial bent--

00:50:05.552 --> 00:50:07.010 align:middle line:84%
>>JAY: Which you're
not, of course.

00:50:07.010 --> 00:50:08.690 align:middle line:84%
>>HOAGLAND: Well,
I-- you know, there

00:50:08.690 --> 00:50:13.380 align:middle line:84%
are rumors out there-- I would
think that movie was designed

00:50:13.380 --> 00:50:15.230 align:middle line:84%
and written and
produced and directed

00:50:15.230 --> 00:50:18.210 align:middle line:84%
and put out there by
someone who understood this.

00:50:18.210 --> 00:50:20.550 align:middle line:84%
Remember, Hollywood
is a huge font.

00:50:20.550 --> 00:50:23.000 align:middle line:84%
Well, you've analyzed
Kubrick to death.

00:50:23.000 --> 00:50:25.490 align:middle line:84%
Hollywood is where the
truth is being told.

00:50:25.490 --> 00:50:28.150 align:middle line:84%
But, as Emily Dickinson used
to say, "tell all the truth,

00:50:28.150 --> 00:50:29.509 align:middle line:90%
but tell it slant."

00:50:29.509 --> 00:50:30.925 align:middle line:84%
They don't tell
it to us directly.

00:50:30.925 --> 00:50:32.890 align:middle line:90%
They tell it to us in symbology.

00:50:32.890 --> 00:50:35.280 align:middle line:84%
And Jim Carrey's
"Liar Liar" I think

00:50:35.280 --> 00:50:38.590 align:middle line:84%
was perfectly made for
the consciousness effects

00:50:38.590 --> 00:50:42.470 align:middle line:84%
of this physics on people now
who are more and more inspired

00:50:42.470 --> 00:50:45.945 align:middle line:90%
or impelled to tell their truth.

00:50:45.945 --> 00:50:47.207 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: Well, that sounds good.

00:50:47.207 --> 00:50:48.790 align:middle line:84%
So we're going to
go to Facebook here.

00:50:48.790 --> 00:50:50.220 align:middle line:90%
We've got a few minutes left.

