00:51:12.710 --> 00:51:14.626 align:middle line:84%
>>JAY: And the Mayans
were obsessed with them.

00:51:14.626 --> 00:51:18.360 align:middle line:84%
>>HOAGLAND: Obsessed with
the position of the Pleiades.

00:51:18.360 --> 00:51:21.480 align:middle line:84%
The relationship between
the Pleiades and Venus

00:51:21.480 --> 00:51:23.910 align:middle line:90%
is important in Mayan cosmology.

00:51:23.910 --> 00:51:26.390 align:middle line:84%
The Pleiades themselves
are relatively close.

00:51:26.390 --> 00:51:28.700 align:middle line:90%
They're 420 light years away.

00:51:28.700 --> 00:51:30.920 align:middle line:84%
Remember, alignments
in the physics

00:51:30.920 --> 00:51:32.690 align:middle line:90%
cause a tremor in the force.

00:51:32.690 --> 00:51:36.340 align:middle line:84%
I've actually tried to measure
a close approach of the moon

00:51:36.340 --> 00:51:39.150 align:middle line:84%
