00:51:48.800 --> 00:51:52.130 align:middle line:84%
But there are hints
that there are effects.

00:51:52.130 --> 00:51:55.850 align:middle line:84%
Because of the unique geometry
of this solar eclipse,

00:51:55.850 --> 00:51:57.930 align:middle line:84%
we might see something
in the data that

00:51:57.930 --> 00:52:00.290 align:middle line:84%
would allow us to speak
more to her question.

00:52:00.290 --> 00:52:02.370 align:middle line:84%
But it's a very
perceptive question.

00:52:02.370 --> 00:52:04.280 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: I agree.

