the other day--

00:52:26.910 --> 00:52:29.410 align:middle line:90%
a new dawn on the horizon.

00:52:29.410 --> 00:52:32.510 align:middle line:84%
The symbology being
spoken about at levels,

00:52:32.510 --> 00:52:34.240 align:middle line:84%
like they're talking
to other audiences

00:52:34.240 --> 00:52:36.840 align:middle line:90%
to alert them to what's coming.

00:52:36.840 --> 00:52:38.960 align:middle line:84%
The Mayans were not
predicting catastrophe.

00:52:38.960 --> 00:52:41.760 align:middle line:84%
John is right--
John Major Jenkins.

00:52:41.760 --> 00:52:46.120 align:middle line:84%
They predicted
change, a revelation,

00:52:46.120 --> 00:52:48.100 align:middle line:90%
a lifting of the veil.

00:52:48.100 --> 00:52:51.480 align:middle line:84%
The physical problems we've had,
like earthquakes, tornadoes,

00:52:51.480 --> 00:52:53.980 align:middle line:84%
and all that-- remember, that's
part of the physics, too.

00:52:53.980 --> 00:52:57.530 align:middle line:84%
The planet is adjusting
to the new torsion field.

00:52:57.530 --> 00:52:59.510 align:middle line:84%
And like with any
mechanical system,

00:52:59.510 --> 00:53:03.880 align:middle line:84%
it has aches and
springs and whatever.

00:53:03.880 --> 00:53:08.230 align:middle line:84%
Carl Sagan used to say that
what is trivial to the planet

00:53:08.230 --> 00:53:11.810 align:middle line:84%
has huge effects for beagles
and begonias on the planet.

00:53:11.810 --> 00:53:15.020 align:middle line:84%
So, yeah, in the grand
scheme of things,

00:53:15.020 --> 00:53:17.180 align:middle line:84%
no, the human race is not
going to be wiped out.

00:53:17.180 --> 00:53:19.660 align:middle line:84%
But in the short term,
you need to pay attention

00:53:19.660 --> 00:53:20.694 align:middle line:90%
to where you live.

00:53:20.694 --> 00:53:22.110 align:middle line:84%
If you live in an
earthquake zone,

00:53:22.110 --> 00:53:25.110 align:middle line:84%
like Japan, during the
Fukushima earthquake,

00:53:25.110 --> 00:53:27.440 align:middle line:84%
that was not a good
place to put a reactor.

00:53:27.440 --> 00:53:28.070 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: No.

00:53:28.070 --> 00:53:31.375 align:middle line:84%
>>HOAGLAND: How idiotic to put
reactors in all continents next

00:53:31.375 --> 00:53:33.460 align:middle line:84%
to earthquake
zones, particularly

00:53:33.460 --> 00:53:36.870 align:middle line:84%
if the tremors in
the force get bigger

00:53:36.870 --> 00:53:39.410 align:middle line:84%
and you basically
change plate structure

00:53:39.410 --> 00:53:42.320 align:middle line:84%
and you have entropy
dislocations, i.e.,

00:53:42.320 --> 00:53:43.590 align:middle line:90%
called earthquakes.

00:53:43.590 --> 00:53:45.340 align:middle line:84%
I thought it was
interesting the other day

