that Prince Charles,
when he was in Scotland--

00:53:48.890 --> 00:53:50.300 align:middle line:84%
remember what
Scotland represents

00:53:50.300 --> 00:53:54.740 align:middle line:84%
in the symbology-- Scottish
Rite Masons and all

00:53:54.740 --> 00:53:58.191 align:middle line:84%
