weather forecast.

00:53:58.191 --> 00:53:59.190 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: Yeah, I saw that.

00:53:59.190 --> 00:54:00.610 align:middle line:84%
>>HOAGLAND: Why was
he doing the weather?

00:54:00.610 --> 00:54:01.600 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: Very amusing.

00:54:01.600 --> 00:54:04.600 align:middle line:84%
>>HOAGLAND: I think it was
part of this secret code

00:54:04.600 --> 00:54:06.680 align:middle line:84%
that weather is one
of the things being

00:54:06.680 --> 00:54:08.980 align:middle line:90%
impacted by this physics.

00:54:08.980 --> 00:54:14.480 align:middle line:84%
Those tornadoes in Alabama were
stunning, devastating, totally

00:54:14.480 --> 00:54:15.100 align:middle line:90%
out of season.

00:54:15.100 --> 00:54:16.516 align:middle line:84%
>>JAY: Well, England
also has been

00:54:16.516 --> 00:54:19.247 align:middle line:84%
going through the coldest
spring in 150 years.

00:54:19.247 --> 00:54:20.080 align:middle line:90%
>>HOAGLAND: Exactly.

00:54:20.080 --> 00:54:21.246 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: In fact, it's winter.

00:54:21.246 --> 00:54:22.270 align:middle line:90%
>>HOAGLAND: Yep.

00:54:22.270 --> 00:54:24.270 align:middle line:84%
But you see, these
are only problems

00:54:24.270 --> 00:54:27.440 align:middle line:84%
if you don't socially
understand what's causing them

00:54:27.440 --> 00:54:29.450 align:middle line:84%
and take steps to
prepare for them.

00:54:29.450 --> 00:54:32.000 align:middle line:84%
We need to become more
conscious, all of us,

00:54:32.000 --> 00:54:34.670 align:middle line:84%
that these are natural
parts of this cycle.

00:54:34.670 --> 00:54:35.695 align:middle line:90%
They can be dealt with.

00:54:35.695 --> 00:54:37.195 align:middle line:84%
The planet's not
going to disappear.

00:54:37.195 --> 00:54:39.410 align:middle line:84%
We're not going to lose
billions of people.

00:54:39.410 --> 00:54:40.690 align:middle line:90%
That's fear porn.

00:54:40.690 --> 00:54:42.340 align:middle line:84%
What we are going
to do, however,

